lines.text: Aus 5 ( 4 ) Consider proper cloud type to be used.
- This is the most basie yet most important
aspect as according to the usage
of the user the specific cloud type should
be selected from Public / Private or
Hybrid clouds.
for Example:
if a user wants to host a blog them
he must go for public cloud , if the
want's some finance related application
then he must go for Private cloud,
if he wants both the functionalities them
he must go for Hyperid cloud.
